<div class="header hero">
    <div class="row columns spacer"></div>
    <div class="row columns">
        <h1>Se (re)mettre <b>au sport</b>,<br/>
        n’a jamais été <b>aussi simple</b>.</h1>
        <h2>Réservez des scéances de sport près de chez vous : <br/>
        sans engagement, ni abonnement.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row mainsearch">
        <div class="columns large-8 large-centered small-collapse">
            <div class="small-4 medium-3 columns">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Aïkido" data-open="joinUs" (click)="showJoinUs()" />
            </div>
            <div class="small-4 medium-3 columns">
                <input type="text" placeholder="16.09.2016" data-open="joinUs" (click)="showJoinUs()" />
            </div>
            <div class="small-4 medium-3 columns">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Nantes" data-open="joinUs" (click)="showJoinUs()" />
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-3 columns spaced">
                <input type="submit" class="button expanded" value="GO !" (click)="showJoinUs()"
                        data-open="joinUs"
                        data-ga-category="popupLaunch"
                        data-ga-action="Nav click"
                        data-ga-label="Search" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="suggestion">
    <div class="row">
        <h3 class="text-center">Par temps froids,<br/> rien de mieux que des scéances toutes en douceur !</h3>
        <p class="subheader">Notre selection du mois de novembre :</p>
    </div>
    <div class="row suggestion__list row small-up-1 medium-up-3">
        <div class="column" (click)="showJoinUs()" data-open="joinUs"
                data-ga-category="popupLaunch"
                data-ga-action="Nav click"
                data-ga-label="Aquagym">
                <img src="assets/img/aquagym.jpg" class="thumbnail" />
                <p class="thumbnail-title">Aquagym</p>
        </div>
        <div class="column" (click)="showJoinUs()" data-open="joinUs"
                data-ga-category="popupLaunch"
                data-ga-action="Nav click"
                data-ga-label="Pilates">
                <img src="assets/img/pilates.jpg" class="thumbnail" />
                <p class="thumbnail-title">Pilates</p>
        </div>
        <div class="column" (click)="showJoinUs()" data-open="joinUs"
                data-ga-category="popupLaunch"
                data-ga-action="Nav click"
                data-ga-label="Yoga">
                <img src="assets/img/yoga.jpg" class="thumbnail" />
                <p class="thumbnail-title">Yoga</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="reveal hollow" data-reveal id="subscribe_confirmation">
    <h2><b>Pré-inscription validée :</b><br/>
    on revient très vite vers vous !</h2>
    <p class="trigger"><em>Juste le temps de faire un tour,<br/>
    sur les réseaux sociaux :</em></p>
    <div class="row small-collapse sociallinks">
        <div class="large-4 columns">

            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Bemoove.fr/" data-ga-category="Outbound links" data-ga-action="After Subscribe" data-ga-label="Facebook" target="_blank" data-social="facebook" class="js-social-link"><img src="assets/img/facebook.png" alt="facebook" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="large-4 columns text-center">
            <a href="https://twitter.com/Bemoove" data-ga-category="Outbound links" data-ga-action="After Subscribe" data-ga-label="Twitter" target="_blank" data-social="twitter" class="js-social-link"><img src="assets/img/twitter.png" alt="twitter" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="large-4 columns text-right">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/bemoovefr/" data-ga-category="Outbound links" data-ga-action="After Subscribe" data-ga-label="Instagram" target="_blank" data-social="instagram" class="js-social-link"><img src="assets/img/instagram.png" alt="instagram" /></a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center">
        <p class="seeyou">À bientôt !</p>
        <img src="assets/img/bemoove-tiny-logo.png" class="tiny-logo" />
    </div>
</div>
